        public void sendNotification(String destinationName,
                             Object message,
                             String subject)
        Convenience method that sends a notification with the given message and subject to the destination. The subject is sent as header as defined in the SNS message JSON formats.
        Parameters:
        destinationName - The logical name of the destination
        message - The message to send
        subject - The subject to send

      • sendNotification

        public void sendNotification(Object message,
                             String subject)
        Convenience method that sends a notification with the given message and subject to the destination. The subject is sent as header as defined in the SNS message JSON formats. The configured default destination will be used.
        Parameters:
        message - The message to send
        subject - The subject to send
